translations: n.委托人；代表（commissary 的过去式）

sentences.sentence: They are employed in restaurants, hotels, hospitals and other health care institutions, central food commissaries, clubs and similar establishments, and on ships.
sentences.translation: 他们受雇于餐馆，酒店，医院和其他医疗机构，中央食品小卖部，俱乐部及类似机构，以及船舶上。

sentences.sentence: They are employed in restaurants, hotels, hospitals and other health care institutions, central food commissaries, educational institutions and other establishments.
sentences.translation: 他们受雇于餐厅，宾馆，医院和其他医疗机构，中央食品小卖部，教育机构和其他机构。
